User Management Settings:
——————————————————————————————————————————
User -> User Management Settings

Highly suggested is eo enable enhanced profile user interface
	this will alow the profile page (setup search -> profiles to look a lot more clean 


Other settings that are under user settings can be found here
	-allow external users to deactivate their own accounts
	-hide personal info fields in user records from external users
	-allow user personal dataa to not be recognized in salesforce 
	-etc
